" Hacks

" This is a hack to hide the numbers on the vertical bar,
" so, using the terminal emulator capabilities, it is possible to copy/paste.
" Copy to clipboard without +clipboard
" :h <lt>
noremap <leader><lt>  :set nornu! nonu!<CR>

